0 1 2 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 12l0 .01\"></path><path d=\"M3 13a20 20 0 0 0 18 0\"></path></svg><span>Projects</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium transition-colors text-[var(--text-secondary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\" href=\"/investments\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-5 w-5 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M3 12m0 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1z\"></path><path d=\"M9 8m0 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v10a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1z\"></path><path d=\"M15 4m0 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v14a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-4a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1z\"></path></svg><span>Investments</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium transition-colors text-[var(--text-secondary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\" href=\"/resume\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-5 w-5 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4\"></path><path d=\"M17 21h-10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-14a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M9 9l1 0\"></path><path d=\"M9 13l6 0\"></path><path d=\"M9 17l6 0\"></path></svg><span>Resume</span></a></li><li><a class=\"flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-3 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium transition-colors text-[var(--text-secondary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\" href=\"/contact\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-5 w-5 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-10z\"></path><path d=\"M3 7l9 6l9 -6\"></path></svg><span>Contact</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div></header><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><main id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\" aria-label=\"Portfolio Content\" tabindex=\"-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[var(--surface-primary)] page-section\"><div class=\"page-shell\"><div class=\"space-y-4 max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Projects</span></div><h1 class=\"font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.02]\">Projects across product, analytics, and platform work.</h1><p class=\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose section-subtitle mb-0\">A collection of projects spanning high-scale platforms, analytics work, and investment research experiences.</p></div><div class=\"mb-14 mt-12\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">Featured projects</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><a href=\"/investments\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer group h-full overflow-hidden shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"space-y-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Project</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">2025</span></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Investment Analytics Platform</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] line-clamp-3\">Full-stack investment platform with live Yahoo Finance data — portfolio tracking, gain/loss analytics, and side-by-side stock comparison with 30+ metrics and analyst consensus ratings.</p><div class=\"space-y-1 border-l-2 border-[var(--border-primary)] pl-3\"><p class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">Role: <!-- -->Full-Stack Developer &amp; Designer</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Live data · 30+ metrics per stock · Analyst consensus ratings</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Next.js</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">TypeScript</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Yahoo Finance API</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">+<!-- -->1</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors pt-2\">View project<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div></div></a><a href=\"/fantasy-football\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer group h-full overflow-hidden shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"space-y-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Project</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">2024–2025</span></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Fantasy Football Analytics Platform</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] line-clamp-3\">Full-stack fantasy football platform with live tier rankings, D3 visualizations, and an automated data pipeline.</p><div class=\"space-y-1 border-l-2 border-[var(--border-primary)] pl-3\"><p class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">Role: <!-- -->Solo Builder</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Live platform · 2026 season coming soon</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Next.js</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">D3.js</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">TypeScript</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">+<!-- -->1</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors pt-2\">View project<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></div></div></div></a><a href=\"/fintech-tools/interchange-iq\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer group h-full overflow-hidden shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"space-y-4 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">Project</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">2025</span></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Interchange IQ — Payment Fee Analyzer</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] line-clamp-3\">Interactive tool that models real payment processing costs across 7 major processors using published 2024 interchange rate data. Adjust volume, avg ticket, and card mix to see live fee comparisons and a breakeven analysis.</p><div class=\"space-y-1 border-l-2 border-[var(--border-primary)] pl-3\"><p class=\"text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\">Role: <!-- -->Builder</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">7 processors · Real interchange data · Breakeven calc</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Next.js</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">TypeScript</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">React</span><span class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">+<!-- -->1</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors pt-2\">View project<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" strok